name: Diane
description:
I am a very loving and caring Girl, optimist and I want to find my real love! I’m very communicative person, I like making new friends, talking about all possible themes, but most of all I like joking and laughing. I can be faithful friend and gentle partner. I want to be happy woman and can make you feel happy too! i lost my parents in the past and now i am here to search for true love who can feel the space of the happiness they use to give me. I am here for real and looking for the real man as well…
I want my man to be wise, optimistic, jolly, active. At the same time he has to have enough experience to be a head of the family, to lead his woman, to defense their relations. He has to search not “one more girl”, but his only one. Anything more is important to me apart from age because age is nothing but just a number, so i am ready to date a man of any age and he should be so honest because honesty is the rule of the game. I will be happy to meet a man of Any age and who is really family Oriented will be a Bonus because we can easily share much about how we can both move on in life. Having a True love is a Blessing…
